sults.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 self-start md:self-center mt-2 md:mt-0\"><span class=\"bg-surface border border-border px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] text-foreground-muted\">✓ <!-- -->Real-time input detection</span><span class=\"bg-surface border border-border px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] text-foreground-muted\">✓ <!-- -->Stick drift &amp; joystick drift detection</span><span class=\"bg-surface border border-border px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] text-foreground-muted\">✓ <!-- -->Vibration &amp; rumble testing</span><span class=\"bg-surface border border-border px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] text-foreground-muted\">✓ <!-- -->Path tracing &amp; deadzone mapping</span></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\"><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--surface)\"><button style=\"padding:8px 4px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--background);transition:background .15s;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--foreground-muted);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase\">Player #<!-- -->1</span><span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--primary);max-width:110px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap\">Not connected</span></button><button style=\"padding:8px 4px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;transition:background .15s;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--foreground-muted);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase\">Player #<!-- -->2</span><span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--foreground-secondary);max-width:110px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap\">Not connected</span></butto